OL,5, Phillip Schofield says he believes     
OL,6, homophobia has fuelled the coverage    
OL,7, over his workplace affair with a       
OL,8, younger male colleague.                
OL,10,FIn an interview with BBC News, the     
OL,11,Fex-This Morning host apologised for the
OL,12,F"grave error", saying his career was   
OL,13,Fnow over and he had "lost everything". 
OL,15,FBut he said while he would have "been  
OL,16,Fin trouble" over an affair with a      
OL,17,Fwoman, it would not have been such a   
OL,18,F"massive scandal".                     
OL,20,FSchofield came out as gay in 2020.     
